OL,3,CAdolescence star dethrones Kate
OL,4,CWinslet as youngest ever Actor Awards
OL,5,Cwinner
OL,7,FOwen Cooper has won an Actor Award for
OL,8,Fhis role in the Netflix drama
OL,9,FAdolescence, adding to his already
OL,10,Fhistoric collection of trophies.
OL,12,FThe 16-year-old was named best actor
OL,13,Fin a Television Movie or Limited
OL,14,FSeries at the 2026 ceremony on Sunday,
OL,15,Fbut was not present to collect his
OL,16,Faward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
