OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772451406
OL,3,CAdolescence star dethrones Kate
OL,4,CWinslet as youngest ever Actor Awards
OL,5,Cwinner
OL,7,FFormerly known as the Screen Actors
OL,8,FGuild Awards (SAG), Cooper has
OL,9,Fofficially dethroned Kate Winslet as
OL,10,Fthe youngest-ever individual winner at
OL,11,Fthe event. Winslet was 20 when she won
OL,12,Ffor Sense and Sensibility in 1996.
OL,14,FPresenters Damson Idris and Yerin Ha
OL,15,Fannounced the win, with Idris joking:
OL,16,F"Owen couldn't be here so I'll be
OL,17,Ftaking this home, thank you."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
