PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772451406
OL,3,CAdolescence star dethrones Kate
OL,4,CWinslet as youngest ever Actor Awards
OL,5,Cwinner
OL,7,FThe win completes Cooper's sweep of
OL,8,Fmajor awards this season for his debut
OL,9,Frole as Jamie Miller, a 13-year-old
OL,10,Fmurder suspect in the Netflix
OL,11,Fpsychological thriller Adolescence.
OL,13,FThe four-part limited series, co-
OL,14,Fcreated by Stephen Graham and Jack
OL,15,FThorne, gained massive critical
OL,16,Facclaim for its "one-shot" style. Each
OL,17,Fhour-long episode is filmed in a
OL,18,Fsingle, continuous take.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
