OL,3,CAdolescence star dethrones Kate
OL,4,CWinslet as youngest ever Actor Awards
OL,5,Cwinner
OL,7,FCooper, who is from Warrington, beat
OL,8,Fout Jason Bateman, his co-star Stephen
OL,9,FGraham, Charlie Hunnam and Matthew
OL,10,FRhys, adding to his increasing
OL,11,Fcollection of trophies.
OL,13,FOver the past six months, the young
OL,14,Factor has claimed:
OL,16,FCooper recently made his feature film
OL,17,Fdebut as Young Heathcliff in Emerald
OL,18,FFennell's adaptation of Wuthering
OL,19,FHeights, starring alongside Margot
OL,20,FRobbie and Jacob Elordi.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
