OL,3,CAdolescence star dethrones Kate
OL,4,CWinslet as youngest ever Actor Awards
OL,5,Cwinner
OL,7,FHe is also set to appear in the
OL,8,Fupcoming Tom Ford drama Cry to Heaven,
OL,9,Falongside the likes of Aaron Taylor-
OL,10,FJohnson, Colin Firth and Nicholas
OL,11,FHoult.
OL,13,FListen to the ITV News entertainment
OL,14,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
